description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do you really want to make a difference? Very Special Recovery Focussed Service needs Very Special Business Data Officer You!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Data Officer Band 4&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We may be able to support flexible working to suit you ! Incentives to join us available!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Inclusion Drug Alcohol Services&lt;/strong&gt;has a reputation for &lt;strong&gt;QUALITY&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;INNOVATIVE&lt;/strong&gt; services to substance misusers in the community and criminal justice settings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working in a busy community service such as ours can obviously be &lt;strong&gt;challenging &lt;/strong&gt;at times but equally &lt;strong&gt;rewarding&lt;/strong&gt; and no two days are the same. Do you have the passion, motivation and energy to join our &lt;strong&gt;incredibly friendly and supportive team&lt;/strong&gt; ?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will an experianced data administrator, you will be able to work under pressure in a busy substance misuse service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It goes without saying that you will also need excellent communication, negotiation, networking and interpersonal skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are energised by our vision of an entrepreneurial NHS focused on tackling social exclusion, please come and discuss with us how our needs might match your aspirations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion please contact Tracy Braddock - Service Manager Tel: 07773966355.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As an NHS employer we offer an excellent employment package including:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Excellent salary pension scheme&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Generous annual leave&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Incremental salary scales&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Great training opportunities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Occupational health and staff support systems&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
